<h2><a name="isdigit" id="isdigit">isdigit</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Синтаксис:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cctype&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">int</span> isdigit<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> ch <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
<p>

Функция isdigit() возвращяет ненулевое значение если её аргумент является цифрой. Иначе возвращает ноль.
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">     <span class="kw4">char</span> c<span class="sy0">;</span>
     scanf<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;%c&quot;</span><span class="sy0">,</span> <span class="sy0">&amp;</span>c <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span>
     <span class="kw1">if</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> isdigit<span class="br0">&#40;</span>c<span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>
       <a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/printf.html"><span class="kw3">printf</span></a><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="st0">&quot;You entered the digit %c<span class="es1">\n</span>&quot;</span><span class="sy0">,</span> c <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy0">;</span></pre>
